author: Play On Tabletop
description:
Thank you to Combat Cards for sponsoring this episode!  Combat cards is a tactical game where you build your deck of heroes from the 41st millennium and try your hand against other players and pre made campaigns.  Mubin has created one he challenges anyone to beat!

August is the 6th birthday of combat cards and we will be celebrating with lots of events, community challenges, prizes and much more! The celebrations ingame will start on the 8th August.  ALSO! Redeem code - TITAN - for 60 plasma, 600 coins and 60 cards. Nice!

===============GAME INFO=============
The new Grey Knight Codex has been released and Micael is here to be the "good guys" for a change and fight the dastardly Thousand Sons piloted by our own Mubin.  Both armies feature heavy use of psychically gifted individuals and brutal power armour.  Who will come up on top?  Let's find out!
===============ARMY LIST=============
Mubin - Thousand Sons - Rubricae Phalanx

CHARACTER

Daemon Prince of Tzeentch with Wings - Warlo
title: Grey Knights vs Thousand Sons : Psyker Duel! - 40k in 40m Warhammer Battle
